"Pumpkin Pie Lust pours a hazy deep brown color with a small but long lasting lacing head.  There is a very mellow aroma, with hints of cinnamon and pumpkin.  The taste has pumpkin flavors, hints of cinnamon and all spice.  Good body, weaker flavors.  Overall its a very easy drinking pumpkin ale, lighter flavors, but still enjoyable."
