"Pours deep wood brown with a haze and a finger and a half billowing fluffy tan head that retain nicely. Smell has pumpkin wheat and nutty malt aromas forward along woth a slightly musty smell. Some light cinnamon, nutmeg, and spice aromas are on the back end. Taste has more musty pumpkin and sweet malt flavors forward followed by an interesting flavor I can only describe as coca cola. Light spice flavors of cinnamon and nutmeg in the finish. Medium light body is cut by high carbonation."
